---
title: Creamy Butter Bean and Pepper Rice Bowl with Cheese and Pesto Drizzle
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Butter Bean and Pepper Stew in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R17_W19_UK_QV12039-9_Main__2low-548ee2e2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/65ef17eba66a6a1427fc264d.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/creamy-butter-bean-and-pepper-rice-bowl-65ef17eba66a6a1427fc264d
author: Mimi Morley
cuisine: Italian
